      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting an exemplary specimen maintained to an uncompromising standard. This vehicle remains in showroom condition, exhibiting no discernible wear and reflecting a history of fastidious care. A rare opportunity for the discerning collector to acquire a truly pristine asset that transcends the typical secondary market offering. Inspection will reveal a vehicle that is, in every measurable sense, indistinguishable from new.",
