    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a ride that looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor? This absolute beauty is in mint condition and has been my pride and joy. I've pampered it from day one\u2014not a single scratch or speck of dust to be found! It drives like a total dream and is ready for its next big adventure. You've really got to see it to believe how pristine it is. Come check it out and let's get you behind the wheel!",
      "price": 46500.0,
