      "timestep_posted": 5
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Available is a pristine E46 M3, a benchmark of Bavarian engineering. This specimen features the high-revving S54 3.2L straight-six, delivering linear power through six individual throttle bodies and optimized Double VANOS. The drivetrain is anchored by a Getrag 420G manual transmission and a factory M-Variable limited-slip differential. Maintenance is exhaustive: the rear subframe has been reinforced, and rod bearings were replaced as a preventative measure. The suspension retains its factory-fresh damping characteristics and bushing integrity. With flawless paint depth and a perfectly preserved interior, this unit represents a turnkey investment for the discerning collector.",
